<title>USA: Broadway &amp; Seymour gets $15 mln credit line.</title>
<headline>Broadway &amp; Seymour gets $15 mln credit line.</headline>
<dateline>CHARLOTTE, N.C. 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Broadway &amp; Seymour Inc said on Thursday it entered a $15 million credit facility with Fleet National Bank of Boston.</p>
<p>Based on operating expectations, Broadway said it did not expect to draw on the facility in the near-term.</p>
<p>Broadway &amp; Seymour is a industry-specialized software and services company.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-1730))</p>
